When Prince of Yuzhang was escorting
the officials into the Capital,

121
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:47,960
they were attacked by assassins.

122
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:50,240
But Prince of Yuzhang wrote
that he was prepared,

123
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,600
and not a single official was injured.

124
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:56,200
- Not a single one?
- Yes.

125
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:59,640
I'm afraid
that even if there were casualties,

126
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:01,840
he wouldn't dare let me know.

127
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:03,040
Besides,

128
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:06,080
the one accompanying him into the Capital
wasn't Shi Yan, but Zhong Lin.

129
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,560
She must be coming to see Cangcang, right?

130
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:12,640
It's fine.

131
00:15:13,280 --> 00:15:15,960
It's about time
Cangcang saw an old friend.

132
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:18,800
WUYING HALL

133
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:25,520
Preceptor Du.

134
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:30,560
Eunuch Feng.

135
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,960
May I ask

136
00:15:34,040 --> 00:15:35,920
where His Majesty has just come back from?

137
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:37,560
Linghe Hall.

138
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:49,600
I can manage on my own. I'm fine.

139
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:52,960
His Majesty specifically instructed us
to be extra careful with your right arm.

140
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:54,880
So, please let me serve you.

141
00:16:00,680 --> 00:16:02,000
Is His Majesty

142
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:03,760
all right?

143
00:16:03,840 --> 00:16:05,560
His Majesty missed his medicine,

144
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:07,800
then spent his inner strength
purging the poison from you,

145
00:16:07,880 --> 00:16:09,240
and even took a sword strike from you.

146
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:10,600
His condition is very serious.

147
00:16:11,920 --> 00:16:13,880
Your Majesty, Preceptor Du barged in…

148
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:17,160
Du Tingxin of Nanrong Palace
pays respects to Your Majesty.

149
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:19,280
Rise, Preceptor Du.

150
00:16:23,680 --> 00:16:24,720
Leave it to me.

151
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:29,680
Xiaoshan, you all may go.

152
00:16:30,280 --> 00:16:31,520
- Got it.
- Got it.

153
00:16:39,560 --> 00:16:41,480
You came in person.

154
00:16:41,560 --> 00:16:44,320
Something major happened the day
before yesterday?

155
00:16:46,400 --> 00:16:49,320
You were controlled
by Princess Ying's Puppet Incense

156
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:51,920
and tried to stab His Majesty.

157
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:58,600
But you dislocated your own arm

158
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:01,200
to keep His Majesty safe.

159
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:13,079
You came in person just to tell me this?

160
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:16,000
Your Majesty is perceptive.

161
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:19,640
Then I won't hide anything.

162
00:17:22,319 --> 00:17:23,560
Are you aware

163
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:25,319
of my background?

164
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:27,280
Please enlighten me.

165
00:17:29,360 --> 00:17:32,360
I'm the former Preceptor's daughter,
not her disciple.

166
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:36,800
An Imperial Preceptor
was supposed to live a spotless life.

167
00:17:38,080 --> 00:17:40,920
But she had an affair with another man
and secretly gave birth to me.

168
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:44,280
She raised me as her "disciple".

169
00:17:47,560 --> 00:17:48,880
Later, when the truth came out,

170
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:52,560
my mother was forced
to burn herself alive to atone.

171
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:56,160
Her only wish was to keep me safe.

172
00:17:57,640 --> 00:17:59,000
But the ministers

173
00:17:59,560 --> 00:18:01,160
still wouldn't let it go.

174
00:18:04,120 --> 00:18:05,920
<i>I was hiding in the shrine that day.</i>

175
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:07,240
<i>This girl</i>

176
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:09,880
<i>is an affront to Heaven and our ancestors.</i>

177
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:11,560
<i>She has no right to live.</i>

178
00:18:12,080 --> 00:18:13,440
<i>She should be sacrificed to Heaven!</i>

179
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:35,760
Don't be afraid.

180
00:18:36,280 --> 00:18:38,880
Today, I exercised my right to pardon.

181
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:40,400
From this day on,

182
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,720
you are the new Imperial Preceptor.

183
00:18:41,800 --> 00:18:43,640
Why did my master

184
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:46,800
name the shrine "Nanrong Palace"?

185
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:48,400
Did she think

186
00:18:48,480 --> 00:18:50,680
I was unwelcome to the world?

187
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:52,000
Even if the world rejects you,

188
00:18:52,080 --> 00:18:54,040
you must fight to live.

189
00:18:54,560 --> 00:18:56,520
The former Preceptor burned herself alive.

190
00:18:56,600 --> 00:18:59,000
Isn't this the very result she sought?

191
00:19:13,240 --> 00:19:14,800
<i>That day, when His Majesty took my hand</i>

192
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:17,840
and led me out of Nanrong Palace,

193
00:19:20,080 --> 00:19:21,480
I made up my mind

194
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:25,920
that my whole life
would belong to him alone.

195
00:19:31,360 --> 00:19:33,200
If His Majesty can be
with the one he loves,

196
00:19:34,040 --> 00:19:35,320
that is the greatest joy I could ask for.

197
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:39,680
You don't actually think

198
00:19:39,760 --> 00:19:41,840
the one His Majesty loves is me, do you?

199
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:45,600
Why are you so certain it isn't?

200
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:56,040
Emperors are heartless.

201
00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:58,000
In the end,

202
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,200
power is all he's ever valued.

203
00:20:02,440 --> 00:20:04,040
I came here today

204
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:07,040
because the night before last,

205
00:20:07,120 --> 00:20:08,640
you were under someone else's control,

206
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:11,600
yet you chose to injure yourself
rather than harm His Majesty.

207
00:20:12,600 --> 00:20:13,680
I believe

208
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:16,400
Your Majesty

209
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:18,760
might truly care for him after all.

210
00:20:31,520 --> 00:20:34,120
I beg Your Majesty
to give His Majesty a little trust.

211
00:20:35,280 --> 00:20:37,720
If affection can grow between you,

212
00:20:37,800 --> 00:20:39,080
then Nanrong Palace

213
00:20:39,600 --> 00:20:42,000
will be Linghe Hall's most loyal ally.

214
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:47,400
And if I can't?

215
00:20:50,240 --> 00:20:51,360
I should say no more.

216
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:53,360
Such words would be overstepping.

217
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:58,560
Your Majesty is still recovering,

218
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:00,360
so I will take my leave.

219
